    "A subject said \"I like the counseling part of the system.",
    "The tone is supportive and encouraging.The system really understands what I said to it and provides reasonable and applicable guides\" (S08).",
    "In addition, a few subjects find the guidance (Guide feature) provided by CaiTI during the psychotherapies helpful.",
    "\"To be honest, I was not that familiar with what they called the CBT procedures at the end of each conversation.",
    "Initially, I did not know what are the \"unhelpful thoughts\" in my situations."
